data.description: COUNT YOUR BLESSINGS!! Large home just waiting for you. This 4 Bedroom 2.5 Baths property has many features to please you and yours. Enter into a large entry way with sitting area to your left and half bath to your right with an office, hobby room, entertainment room to your right. Laundry room located on 1st floor for your convenience. Kitchen, Dining area and Family Room has an opened concept. Kitchen features an Island and all appliances. Upstairs you will find all 4 bedroom and 2 baths, 2 linen closets and a large loft. Large Master Bedroom 16' x 19' w/ large Master Bath featuring Garden Tub, double sinks, His and Her Walk-in closets, and a private water closet with commode and shower. Guest Bath has double sinks, tub/shower combo. Other wonderful features of this home is a 3 Car Garage, covered, screened in Lanai. Call today for your appointment to view this property.
